tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE robot_movement (id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    robot_id UUID,
    current_position VARCHAR,
    destination VARCHAR,
    speed FLOAT,
    distance_traveled FLOAT,
    direction VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE navigation_history (
  navigation_id INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  start_location VARCHAR(255),
  end_location VARCHAR(255),
  navigation_type VARCHAR(50)
 );

CREATE TABLE RobotLocations ( 
   robot_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
   location_name VARCHAR(255), 
   x_coordinate FLOAT, 
   y_coordinate FLOAT, 
   timestamp TIMESTAMP 
);

CREATE TABLE RobotPaths ( 
   path_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
   robot_id INT, 
   start_location VARCHAR(255), 
   end_location VARCHAR(255), 
   distance FLOAT, 
   path_time FLOAT 
);

CREATE TABLE RobotLocations (
    location_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    robot_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    latitude DECIMAL,
    longitude DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE RobotStatus (
    status_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    robot_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    battery_status DECIMAL,
    operational_status VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE RobotCommands (
    command_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    robot_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    command_type VARCHAR(50),
    command_data JSON
);
